description: This table compares the proposed algorithm, FOMD-OMS, with two existing federated online multi-kernel learning algorithms, eM-KOFL and POF-MKL.  The comparison includes the regret bound, per-round time complexity on the client, and the communication cost (download).  It highlights that FOMD-OMS achieves a better regret bound and lower computational and communication costs than the other two algorithms.
